2) Collection of funds by the enterprise and replacement of outdated fixed assets with new ones. Nowadays, accelerated depreciation is applied in a number of countries, which, on the one hand, reduces the amount of taxable profit, and on the other hand, enables the enterprise to be equipped with new machinery and equipment.;
